{"word":"ἔξωθεν","slug":"ἔξωθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἔξωϑεν</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔξω\">ἔξω</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> of place <b>outside, on the outside <a href='B:470 23:27'>Mt 23:27f</a>; <a href='B:540 7:5'>2 Cor 7:5</a>; <a href='B:730 11:2'>Rv 11:2b</a></b> (throw/leave out); as noun <b><a href='B:470 23:25'>Mt 23:25</a>; <a href='B:480 4:11'>Mk 4:11</a>; <a href='B:480 7:18'>7:18</a>; <a href='B:490 11:39'>Lk 11:39</a></b><a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ f\">f</a><b>; <a href='B:610 3:7'>1 Ti 3:7</a>; <a href='B:670 3:3'>1 Pt 3:3</a>;</b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:480 7:15'>Mk 7:15</a></b> (from outside); <b><a href='B:730 11:2'>Rv 11:2a</a>; <a href='B:730 14:20'>14:20</a></b> (outside). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔξω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐξωθέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}